This little program can draw the Sierpinski Triangle, either in your console or
as a PNG image.

Written for Python 3.

Requirements are listed in requirements.txt.

Usage:

python triangles.py [console|image] [iterations]

Examples:

$ python triangles.py console 3

                                                          
